================================================================================
                              ATTRIBUTION
================================================================================

SnoopyPower is built upon SCAbox — an open framework for FPGA-based remote
side-channel analysis developed at École des Mines de Saint-Étienne (EMSE).
The TDC sensor and FIFO controller IP cores under hw/ip_repo/ are derived
from SCAbox; the original IP packages preserve their EMSE vendor namespace
(emse.sas:sca:*) inside their component.xml.

Project page:  https://emse-sas-lab.github.io/SCAbox/

The TDC sensor design and original FPGA-based remote SCA methodology are
described in the works listed in CITATION.cff; please cite them when using
SnoopyPower in academic work.
